statements: SELECT * FROM Bioenergy_Research
SELECT researcher_name, energy_output FROM Bioenergy_Research
SELECT id, researcher_name, feedstock_type FROM Bioenergy_Research WHERE energy_output > 100
SELECT * FROM Bioenergy_Research ORDER BY researcher_name ASC
SELECT researcher_name, feedstock_type FROM Bioenergy_Research WHERE id = 3
SELECT DISTINCT researcher_name, feedstock_type FROM Bioenergy_Research WHERE energy_output > 1000 ORDER BY researcher_name DESC
SELECT researcher_name, feedstock_type, energy_output FROM Bioenergy_Research WHERE feedstock_type = 'Biomass' ORDER BY energy_output DESC
SELECT * FROM Bioenergy_Research WHERE energy_output BETWEEN 500 AND 1000 ORDER BY id
SELECT researcher_name, energy_output FROM Bioenergy_Research WHERE energy_output < 500 OR feedstock_type = 'Biofuel' ORDER BY researcher_name, energy_output
SELECT researcher_name, SUM(energy_output) AS total_energy_output FROM Bioenergy_Research GROUP BY researcher_name HAVING SUM(energy_output) > 5000 ORDER BY total_energy_output DESC
SELECT biomass_id, biomass_name, energy_output FROM BiomassFeedstocks;
SELECT * FROM Researchers;
SELECT researcher_name, research_field FROM Researchers ORDER BY researcher_name ASC;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM BiomassFeedstocks;
SELECT researcher_name, affiliation FROM Researchers WHERE research_field = 'Biotechnology';
SELECT * FROM BiomassFeedstocks ORDER BY biomass_id DESC;
SELECT biomass_name, energy_output FROM BiomassFeedstocks WHERE energy_output > 20;
SELECT biomass_name, energy_output FROM BiomassFeedstocks WHERE biomass_id IN (2, 4, 6);
SELECT researcher_name, research_field, affiliation FROM Researchers ORDER BY researcher_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM Researchers WHERE research_field = 'Biotechnology';
SELECT * FROM BiomassFeedstocks;
SELECT feedstock_name, energy_output FROM BiomassFeedstocks WHERE energy_output > 100;
SELECT researcher_name, date_recorded FROM Researchers, ResearchResults WHERE Researchers.researcher_id = ResearchResults.researcher_id;
SELECT result_id, energy_measurement FROM ResearchResults ORDER BY energy_measurement DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS num_results FROM ResearchResults;
SELECT * FROM BiomassFeedstocks;
SELECT feedstock_id, feedstock_name FROM BiomassFeedstocks WHERE energy_output > 1000;
SELECT R.researcher_name, R.affiliation, RR.energy_measurement FROM Researchers R JOIN ResearchResults RR ON R.researcher_id = RR.researcher_id;

SELECT B.feedstock_name, R.researcher_name, RR.energy_measurement FROM BiomassFeedstocks B JOIN Researchers R ON B.feedstock_id = RR.feedstock_id JOIN ResearchResults RR ON R.researcher_id = RR.researcher_id WHERE RR.energy_measurement BETWEEN 2000 AND 5000;

SELECT B.feedstock_name, RR.energy_measurement, RR.date_recorded FROM BiomassFeedstocks B JOIN ResearchResults RR ON B.feedstock_id = RR.feedstock_id WHERE RR.energy_measurement < 5000 ORDER BY RR.date_recorded DESC;
SELECT feedstock_name, energy_output FROM BiomassFeedstocks;
SELECT researcher_name, research_field FROM Researchers;
SELECT project_name, start_date, end_date FROM ResearchProjects;
SELECT feedstock_name, output_date, energy_output FROM BiomassFeedstocks JOIN EnergyOutputs ON BiomassFeedstocks.feedstock_id = EnergyOutputs.feedstock_id;
SELECT project_name, researcher_name, research_field FROM ResearchProjects JOIN Researchers ON ResearchProjects.researcher_id = Researchers.researcher_id;
SELECT * FROM BiomassFeedstocks WHERE energy_output > 50 ORDER BY feedstock_name ASC;
SELECT project_name, researcher_name FROM ResearchProjects JOIN Researchers ON ResearchProjects.researcher_id = Researchers.researcher_id WHERE start_date >= '2023-01-01';

SELECT ResearchProjects.project_name, Researchers.researcher_name, EnergyOutputs.energy_output FROM ResearchProjects JOIN Researchers ON ResearchProjects.researcher_id = Researchers.researcher_id JOIN EnergyOutputs ON ResearchProjects.project_id = EnergyOutputs.project_id WHERE EnergyOutputs.energy_output < 100 ORDER BY start_date DESC;

SELECT BiomassFeedstocks.feedstock_name, EnergyOutputs.energy_output FROM BiomassFeedstocks JOIN EnergyOutputs ON BiomassFeedstocks.feedstock_id = EnergyOutputs.feedstock_id WHERE output_date BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31';

SELECT project_name, COUNT(output_id) AS number_of_outputs FROM ResearchProjects JOIN EnergyOutputs ON ResearchProjects.project_id = EnergyOutputs.project_id GROUP BY project_name HAVING number_of_outputs > 5 ORDER BY number_of_outputs DESC;
SELECT * FROM BiomassFeedstocks;
SELECT biomass_name, energy_output FROM BiomassFeedstocks WHERE biomass_id = 1;
SELECT researcher_name, research_affiliation FROM Researchers WHERE researcher_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM ResearchProjects ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT equipment_name, location FROM LabEquipment;
SELECT * FROM BiomassFeedstocks ORDER BY energy_output DESC;

SELECT researchers.researcher_name, research_projects.project_name, experiment_logs.experiment_date FROM Researchers researchers JOIN ExperimentLogs experiment_logs ON researchers.researcher_id = experiment_logs.researcher_id JOIN ResearchProjects research_projects ON experiment_logs.project_id = research_projects.project_id;
SELECT equipment_name, location FROM LabEquipment WHERE location = 'Lab A';
SELECT biomass_name, energy_output FROM BiomassFeedstocks WHERE energy_output > 5000 ORDER BY energy_output DESC;

SELECT researchers.researcher_name, research_projects.project_name, experiment_logs.experiment_date FROM Researchers researchers JOIN ExperimentLogs experiment_logs ON researchers.researcher_id = experiment_logs.researcher_id JOIN ResearchProjects research_projects ON experiment_logs.project_id = research_projects.project_id ORDER BY experiment_logs.experiment_date DESC;
